    "body": "As I understand your request, you can inject some data in your refinement list with the [`transformItems` option](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/refinement-list/js/#widget-param-transformitems) since [InstantSearch.js 2.10.0](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/develop/CHANGELOG.md#2100-2018-08-08).\r\n\r\nClosing for inactivity – feel free to reopen.",
